Comment: 0,0:23:39.56,0:23:41.94,INJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Again and again, resound again
Comment: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:45.73,INJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Answer refrains in beat of our heart
